66
00:03:05,727 --> 00:03:07,354
It's not your concern anymore.

67
00:03:07,437 --> 00:03:09,981
{\an8}It's nearby. I can feel it.

68
00:03:10,064 --> 00:03:12,442
The powers it bestowed
are on the wane, but...

69
00:03:12,525 --> 00:03:13,568
Enough!

70
00:03:19,198 --> 00:03:22,702
As I was saying, the magics
are losing their potency,

71
