{\an8}but I still have enough to make
short work of the two of you.

72
00:03:29,041 --> 00:03:31,794
{\an8}A quarter of a million dollars per unit.

73
00:03:31,919 --> 00:03:34,756
{\an8}It's hard to believe something so small
could cost so much money...

74
