{\an8}TV REPORTER: <i>Eyewitnesses report the bees</i>

207
00:09:44,626 --> 00:09:46,919
{\an8}<i>have been swarming
the Palmer Tech headquarters</i>

208
00:09:47,003 --> 00:09:48,170
<i>-for the past 20 minutes...</i>
-(COUGHING)

209
00:09:48,254 --> 00:09:50,715
<i>Now all communications in and out
of the building have been cut off.</i>

210
00:09:50,798 --> 00:09:52,091
Have you seen this?

211
00:09:52,424 --> 00:09:55,261
I was just there.
I'd still be there if Felicity hadn't...

212
00:09:56,804 --> 00:09:58,097
Oh my God, Felicity.

213
00:09:58,514 --> 00:09:59,724
(PHONE BEEPING)

214
00:10:02,351 --> 00:10:03,352
(ENGAGED TONE)

215
00:10:05,271 --> 00:10:07,564
But you have a 104 fever.
Where do you think you're going?

216
00:10:07,649 --> 00:10:08,691
{\an8}To get help.

217
00:10:08,775 --> 00:10:10,652
{\an8}I'm pretty sure the police
already know about this.

218
00:10:11,110 --> 00:10:12,444
I'm not talking about the police.

219
00:10:13,487 --> 00:10:16,365
FEMALE REPORTER: <i>We are hearing that SCPD
has sent in an ESU squad.</i>

220
00:10:16,448 --> 00:10:17,950
(SIGHS) Felicity's in there.

221
00:10:18,618 --> 00:10:21,203
Thea, too. I tried calling but no answer.

222
00:10:21,287 --> 00:10:23,455
She must have already been inside
by the time the swarm hit.

223
00:10:23,539 --> 00:10:25,207
-(SIGHS)
-(CELL PHONE VIBRATING)

224
00:10:25,833 --> 00:10:26,959
John's coming in.

225
00:10:27,584 --> 00:10:30,462
This is HIVE, right? There's no way that
this bee attack is a coincidence.

226
00:10:30,546 --> 00:10:33,675
I don't think it's HIVE and I don't think
those are bees.

227
00:10:36,385 --> 00:10:38,971
No. Bees don't give off hundreds
of different kinds of radio frequencies.

228
00:10:39,305 --> 00:10:40,807
Robot bees. Terrific.

229
00:10:40,973 --> 00:10:45,602
Last year, Felicity helped Barry Allen
take down the bees' inventor, Brie Larvan.

230
00:10:45,687 --> 00:10:46,854
So it's payback.

231
00:10:46,938 --> 00:10:49,732
Well, Larvan picked a hell of
a day for it. Donna is in there too.

232
00:10:49,816 --> 00:10:51,734
-What?
-She stopped by Felicity's office to

